summary: Mekhane implementation analysis and gap identification. Maps the 7 axioms/24 theorems/36 derivatives to actual Python implementations in the mekhane directory. Identifies high-density areas (FEP, tekhne-maker, Synedrion) vs gaps (P-series, K1-K3, A-series). Proposes 3-phase implementation plan for 8 new modules including energeia_executor, telos_checker, chronos_evaluator, and others. Includes verification plan and questions for user review.
